<h3><span style="font-size:14px">NAtional SEcurity Directive - by CCS&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-size:14px">telcos to purchse instruments from trusted and certified sources and not china<br />
a. to tackle - trapdoor vulnerabilities<br />
Main directives -<br />
a. classification of tele products as trusted and non trusted<br />
b. to be approved by National security committee - headed by NSA<br />
c. designated authority - national cyber security coordinator&nbsp;<br />
d. telecom companies to purchase from trusted sources</span></p>